5901
// 2E: ADDI $7, $0, 1   (NO SKIP).
31C1
// 30: BNEQ $4, $0, 2   (Branch to 36 if $4 != $0 -> TRUE).
5802
// 32: SKIP (ADDI)
3000
// 34: SKIP (ADDI)
3000

